their passion for the Olympics and sports.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think this is also part of the Olympic spirit \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 to attract more people to participate,\\\" said the 20-year-old, who claimed two golds and one silver for China at the 2022 Winter Olympic Games in Beijing.\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9994810616829609, \"rank\": 0.0003358820478930764, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9933444200823391, \"rank\": 0.006700106311847259, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the torch relay, Gu frequently made a hand gesture representing the number six.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She explained to reporters that in Chinese contemporary slang, \\\"six\\\" signifies being awesome.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the gesture resembles horns, and in Chinese, the character \\\"niu,\\\" meaning \\\"cow,\\\" also means awesome or impressive.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to use this gesture to show that China is awesome, and Chinese athletes are awesome too.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9994810616829609, \"rank\": 0.0003358820478930764, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I especially hope to see Chinese athletes achieve great results in the upcoming Olympics next month,\\\" said Gu.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"score\": 0.9920051957573165, \"rank\": 0.008033897589787953, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_characters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will definitely come to Paris to watch the Olympics then.\\\"\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995982642201, \"rank\": 4.0173587190081287e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a winter sports athlete, Gu would not be drawn on which event she was most looking forward to at the summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not say that.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have many friends competing in the Olympics, and if I mention one and forget another, they might not be happy,\\\" Gu joked.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With her semester at Stanford University having ended, Gu revealed that she had flown for more than 10 hours to France the day before the torch relay and was completing her final assignments on the plane.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"score\": 0.9999864884156213, \"rank\": 1.3498525636753955e-05, \"text\": \"Stanford University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\"}, {\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999845806957715, \"rank\": 1.109101509743473e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have to fly back to the United States tomorrow to continue preparing for my final exams,\\\" Gu said.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999990585329099, \"rank\": 7.152861237946147e-07, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00ac